headline: GoDaddy (GDDY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: GoDaddy has been on fire lately. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has rocketed 49.6%, reaching $206.62 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
